* MULTER
- multer is a very popular middleware to handle multi-part form data, which is a form in coding tha's usd to upload files from a form
 - multer is basically a middleware for multi-part form data
 - We will allow the user to upload a photo on the UpdateMe route
 - install the packaged that we need (npm i multer)
 - on userRoutes.js import multer - follow on that file

 * SHARP
    - npm i sharp
    - sharp is an image processing library for node js
